title: HARVIE TO TELL CONFERENCE OF UNPRECEDENTED ELECTION OPPORTUNITY (Scottish Green Party)
text: ( Source : Scottish Green Party ) Saturday, October 10th , 2015 Patrick Harvie MSP , Co-convener of the Scottish Greens , will today (10 Oct) tell party members at their biggest ever conference that they face an unprecedented election
